  "response": "Here are some unique baby boy names that start with \"Bh\":\n\n1. **Bharat** - Meaning \"India,\" an important character in Indian mythology.\n2. **Bhanu** - Meaning \"sun\" or \"light.\"\n3. **Bhavesh** - Meaning \"lord of the world.\"\n4. **Bhargav** - Another name for Lord Shiva; also means \"brilliant\" or \"sharp.\"\n5. **Bhavik** - Meaning \"well-meaning\" or \"good-hearted.\"\n6. **Bhim** - Meaning \"strong\" or \"powerful,\" often associated with Bhima from the Mahabharata.\n\nYou might also consider variations of these names or look into the cultural significance behind them.",
